## Modules

### 1. Vehicle Registration Module

This module allows users to register their vehicles by providing the driver's name, phone number, vehicle number, and GPS location. The information is stored securely in the MongoDB database.

### 2. Emergency Alert Module

This module enables users to send emergency notifications using the SOS button or by selecting one of the available emergency categories.

Available alert categories include:

- Accident
- Vehicle Crash
- Vehicle Theft
- Natural Disaster
- Fire Hazard
- Flooded Road
- Medical Emergency
- Road Block
- Traffic Congestion
- Animal Crossing
- Low Visibility
- Slippery Road

### 3. Vehicle Activity Module

This module records vehicle activity including login time, logout time, online status, GPS location, and emergency alerts.

### 4. Admin Dashboard Module

The administrator dashboard displays registered vehicles, emergency alerts, accident locations, vehicle status, login history, and allows administrators to manage vehicle records.

