## REST API Endpoints

### Vehicle APIs

POST /register

Registers a new vehicle.

GET /vehicles

Retrieves all registered vehicles.

DELETE /vehicles/:id

Deletes a registered vehicle.

POST /logout

Updates vehicle logout status.

### Alert APIs

POST /alert

Stores emergency alerts.

GET /alerts

Retrieves all emergency alerts.

### Status API

GET /status

Returns the server and database connection status.

